$ Visual Studio platform toolset

The *platform toolset* consists build tools such as
  • compiler
  • linker
  • assembler

It also includes *libraries*.

The binaries are stored in one of the directories below
→ Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Microsoft-Visual-Studio/version/edition/VC/Tools/MSVC/version/bin[`%VSxxxCOMNTOOLS%\MSVC\%VCToolsVersion%\bin`].

In order for these executables to work correctly, some → Windows/development/Visual-Studio/environment-variables[environment variables] need to be set.
